22
00:02:57,100 --> 00:02:59,666
- TELL ME,
WHY DID YOU SHOOT BRANDON?

23
00:03:00,833 --> 00:03:03,833
- BECAUSE HE POINTED
A GUN AT ME.

24
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:23,733
MY NAME IS HARRY MACDOWEL.
I'M THE NEW BOSS OF MILLENNION.

25
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:26,400
FROM NOW ON,
I'LL LIVE FOR THE FAMILY,

26
00:03:26,466 --> 00:03:28,266
AND FIGHT FOR THE FAMILY,

27
00:03:28,333 --> 00:03:31,233
AND BE WILLING TO DIE
FOR THE FAMILY.

28
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:34,300
JUST AS ALL OF YOU
WILL LIVE FOR THE FAMILY,

29
00:03:34,366 --> 00:03:36,333
AND FIGHT FOR THE FAMILY,

30
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:39,066
AND BE WILLING TO DIE
FOR THE FAMILY.

31
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:54,233
- Bob: HEY, LEE.
- YEAH, BOB, WHAT IS IT?

32
00:03:54,300 --> 00:03:55,733
- LEE, YOU KNOW BRANDON.

33
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,433
DO YOU THINK HE BETRAYED
THE ORGANIZATION

34
00:03:57,500 --> 00:03:58,866
THE WAY THEY SAY HE DID?

35
00:03:58,933 --> 00:04:01,400
- I DON'T KNOW. YOU TELL ME.

36
00:04:01,466 --> 00:04:04,366
LISTEN, HARRY KILLS BRANDON,
THEN CALLS HIM A TRAITOR

37
00:04:04,433 --> 00:04:06,000
AND BRANDON CAN'T DENY IT.

38
00:04:06,066 --> 00:04:07,533
THE TRAITOR WAS
HARRY'S BEST FRIEND

39
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,133
BUT HE KILLED HIM ANYWAY.

40
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,866
THAT'S ALL WE REALLY KNOW.

41
00:04:10,933 --> 00:04:13,000
THEN HARRY CLIMBS ANOTHER
RUNG UP THE LADDER

42
00:04:13,066 --> 00:04:14,433
AND HE'LL KEEP ON CLIMBING.

43
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:16,266
HE'LL KEEP GOING TILL
HE GETS TO THE TOP

44
00:04:16,333 --> 00:04:19,533
